            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_001950_0001" n="0001"/>
<lb/><opener><dateline><space extent="2" unit="chars"/><persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Young</persName></dateline>
<lb/><salute><space extent="1" unit="words"/>Dear Sir</salute></opener>
<lb/><p><space extent="4" unit="chars"/>I have been
<lb/>counselled by my
<lb/><term type="tribe"><choice><orig>Makololo</orig><reg>Kololo</reg></choice></term> friends here
<lb/>to send for those
<lb/>of you down about
<lb/>the mission who
<lb/>are it seems numerous
<lb/>enough to carry the
<lb/>boat - and as we
<lb/>are getting on rather
<lb/>slowly and will
<lb/>be glad of anything
<lb/>to expedite the journey
            
	<pb facs="liv_001950_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>I have listened to their
<lb/>advice and written
<lb/>to <persName>Mr Waller</persName> to send
<lb/>40- You will send
<lb/>the accompanying
<lb/>letter down to him
<lb/>and if they come send
<lb/>the <term type="tribe">Ajawa</term> on to me
<lb/>by some who knows 
<lb/>the way - all as
<lb/>quickly as you
<lb/>conveniently can
<lb/>I have mentioned to
<lb/><persName>Waller</persName> the payment
<lb/>I promise to give
<lb/>and he will give you	
        	
	<pb facs="liv_001950_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>a list of the same if they
<lb/>do not prefer waiting
<lb/>till my return - 
<lb/>the calico will be
<lb/>the handkerchief stuff
<lb/>or good prints</p>
<lb/><p>Your deep gully
<lb/>was close at hand
<lb/>when you turned
<lb/>yesterday - we took
<lb/>the way you through
<lb/>&amp; there slept - all
<lb/>this blessed morning
<lb/>handing the beastly
<lb/>thing up the hill - 
<lb/><unclear cert="medium">purchase</unclear> broke by
<lb/>sheer pulling through
<lb/>the sand <add place="inline">^</add> and one<!-- Not entirely certain about this line. -AA --><!-- I have no idea what the VJ is an abbreviation for. JM --><!-- Fixed. AW -->
<lb/><cb/>
<add place="marginleft" rend="vertical">spliced beautifully by Musa and I!!</add>

	<pb facs="liv_001950_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>of the irons <figure><figDesc>Sketch of iron</figDesc></figure> is now
<lb/><figure><figDesc>Sketch of a bent iron</figDesc></figure> - Pole broken
<lb/>at both ends and these
<lb/><choice><sic>thinks</sic><corr>things</corr></choice> may be but a
<lb/>sample <!-- Tweet! -->for the <term type="animal_foodstuff">oxen</term>
<lb/>are not behaving
<lb/>like gentlemen at all
<lb/>We shall in the even
<lb/>of the <term type="tribe">Ajawa</term> coming
<lb/>leave the waggon &amp;
<lb/>the iron can be taken
<lb/>back at your leisure</p>
<lb/><p><persName>David Livingstone</persName>
<lb/><date when="1863-07-17">Thursday 17<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> 2PM</date></p>


            </div>
